article.headline: Drake 86, Morehead St. 70
article.story: DES MOINES, Iowa -- Josh Young scored 34 points and Drake shot 63 percent from the field in the second half to beat Morehead State 86-70 on Wednesday. Young was 7-for-11 from 3-point range for the Bulldogs (1-1), who trailed 39-35 at the half. But Drake made 12 of its first 17 shots after the break, and outscored the Eagles 51-31 in the second half. Bill Eaddy had 17 points and Jonathan Cox added 10 for Drake. The Bulldogs made 15 of 27 3-point shots and 14 of 15 free throws. Morehead State (0-3) got 26 points and eight rebounds from Maze Stallworth. Leon Buchanan added 13 points and Kenneth Faried chipped in 10. Each team finished with 31 rebounds.
